+{{+**EXCEPT/LEAST Variants:** Some inference and viewpoint questions use "EXCEPT" or "LEAST" format. This inverts the task: four answers will be supported by the text, and you must find the one that is NOT. Mark each choice as 'supported' or 'unsupported' to stay organized.+}}

